dsDescriptionValue.value:
The same set of 71 sample tissue microarray (TMA) core images as http://dx.doi.org/10.7910/DVN/RRKMHC, but scanned by a Hamamatsu (C9600 NanoZoomer 2.0-HT) instead of a Zeiss (Axio Scan.Z1) scanner. Each tissue core is named as A_*_PTEN_Hamamatsu.jpg, where * stands for the sample ID.

In addition, 71 corresponding H&E images, named as A_*_HE_ Hamamatsu.jpg, from serial sections were digitized by the same Hamamatsu scanner.
